Class AccessibilityTester.ReportGenerator

java.lang.Object
  |

Direct Known Subclasses:
TextReport, XMLReport
Enclosing class:
AccessibilityTester
public abstract static class AccessibilityTester.ReportGenerator
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract class to generate reports from the tests. A subclass will implement getReport and use the accessor methods to format the results as required.
